All product segements

If you turn off the iPhone segement it is much easier to see how much the iPhone category just dwarves the other parts of Apple's company on the graph. To understand how much the iPhone, Wearables, iPad, Mac, and Services categories actually make it is best to compare them to other stand alone companies as if they were there own individual companies so you can get a better scale of the success of each of them.

Services

Apple has had a focus on dramatcially increases their services revenue over the last several years. They have had several initives that have really helped drive that growth in this category. One of the earlier growth areas was the Apple Music subscription service that started in June 2015.